<div class="hero">
	<div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="hero-logo"><%= image_tag "trimwhitelogo.png" %></span>
		<div class="hero-copy">
			<h1>Mapping Your Food Adventures</h1>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="cards">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-image">
      <%= image_tag "pinsonmap.png" %>
    </div>
    <div class="card-header">
      My NextNoms
    </div>
    <div class="card-copy">
      <p>
        NextNoms is designed to help you keep track of your restaurant bucket list items. Easily visualize where you've eaten and where you want to go next to eat with custom map markers and filtered lists.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-image">
      <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thoughtbot/refills/master/source/images/mountains-4.png" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="card-header">
      Restaurant Roulette
    </div>
    <div class="card-copy">
      <p>Can't decide where to eat? Let Restaurant Roulette pick for you! The Roulette tool will return a random restaurant from your list.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-image">
      <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thoughtbot/refills/master/source/images/mountains-3.png" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="card-header">
      Discover Local Restaurants
    </div>
    <div class="card-copy">
      <p>Looking for local restaurants to add to your NextNoms? Use the Discover tool to find the closest restaurants to your current location!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
